<TEXT>
a woman who has dropped 710 pounds in 
three years is still losing weight through a combination of 
surgery diet and exercise 
i am happy now alive thats how i feel said rosemarie 
carnemolla who has slimmed down to 250 pounds 
carnemolla who lives in union vale about 50 miles north of new 
york city had surgery in 1987 to reduce the size of her stomach 
after 18 months on a liquid diet she began a diet of three meals a 
day with a lot of fruit vegetables and fish 
since her surgery the 5foot4inch carnemolla has seen her 
115inch waist shrink to 44 inches her feet once a size 12eee 
are now a size seven 
i can buy clothes right off the rack theyre big but its 
still something i can go out work take a walk said 
carnemolla who had been a binge eater since childhood 
her weight will drop by 25 pounds next month when doctors 
operate again to cut off excess skin she said 
meanwhile through diet and exercise her weight continues to 
drop carnemollas goal is to get down to 140 pounds 
she swims bowls walks and goes to weight watchers every week 
inspiration has come from diet expert richard simmons carnemolla 
and simmons talk on the telephone several times a week and they 
have appeared on tv shows together 
carnemolla said the more weight she drops the harder it gets to 
lose more 
last week i only lost a pound and a half she said 
thats all right its a pound and a half less than the week 
before 
