of organizations awarded recycled paper products a golden pit 
award for a card illustrated with a vomiting bishop 
that card has since been discontinued said ms thompson the 
irish groups hope the same happens to the rest of the offending 
cards 
well definitely be using the airwaves to make sure nobody 
buys anything from these people said flannelly 
