he would be apprehended 
the worlds no 1 heroin producer maintains his business in 
southeast asias jungles despite repeated thai and burmese military 
strikes clashes with rival drug armies and rumors of fatal 
illness estimates of the size of his private army run from 4000 
to 16000 fighters 
