radicals say real political freedom cannot emerge while 
communist party groups remain in government agencies farms army 
units police precincts and virtually every other institution 
those units give the party control over soviet life and an 
advantage over any new political party 
in remarks carried by the official news agency tass prokofiev 
added that in the proposed law there exists a real basis for 
liquidating the party organizations in businesses and institutions 
