been deeply moved by the idea of a fast 
never before had i been so warmly received everywhere with so 
many positive assurances of help she wrote 
the rev francis x butch mazur a priest at the orchard 
park church urged all who support the hostages to give up 
something of value for the day 
it may mean abstaining from one of the three meals that you 
