pilots licenses after its own investigation showed that the 
cockpit crew boarded the flight within eight hours of drinking the 
federal limit northwest imposes a stricter span of 12 hours 
northwest flight 650 carrying 91 passengers landed safely at 
the minneapolisst paul international airport where the cockpit 
