this years federal deficit will be zero theres no way 
to knock down inflation if the government spends more than it takes 
in he said 
collor de mello also said he would slash import barriers and 
encourage foreign capital 
we will modernize our economy and stimulate competition 
free initiative is the only way to sustained and progressive 
growth he said 
collor de mello issued decrees thursday cutting the number of 
government ministries from 25 to 12 putting up for sale 
governmentowned mansions and cars and preventing public employees 
from holding more than one public job 
initial reaction from conservative politicians and the business 
community to collor de mellos economic measures was positive 
weve worked all our lives for reforms like a balanced budget 
halelujah said conservative sen jarbas pasarinho of the social 
democracy party 
albano franco president of the national confederation of 
industry said the package will allow brazil to escape this 
terrible economic crisis 
