<TEXT>
both the state and exxon figures may be accurate but even the 
best studies of the spills effects are mere snapshots of a rugged 
sparsely populated region the size of new jersey maryland and 
delaware combined 
the coast guard has declared some sort of cleanup must resume 
may 1 but nobody has committed to how much or what kind decisions 
will be made after another survey of beach conditions next month 
in general exposed beaches eroded by winter storms appear to 
